BOOKNOOK  Trademark Information
 The Book Nook, Inc.
Printed publications and printed matter, namely, magazines, journals, books, manuals, diaries, calendars, charts, and printed recipes sold as a component of meal plans, in the fields of health, healthcare, nutrition, diet, weight loss, exercise, fitness, menu planning, and a healthy lifestyle; printed instructional and teaching materials in the fields of health, healthcare, nutrition, diet, weight loss, exercise, fitness, menu planning, and a ...
Electronic retail store services via computer featuring a wide variety of consumer goods, namely, publications, books, magazines, journals, manuals, diaries, and calendars; providing a searchable on-line database via computer featuring consumer information about publications, books, magazines, journals, manuals, diaries, and calendars; providing on line ordering via a computer featuring publications, books, magazines, journals, manuals, diarie...
Delivery services, namely shipping and delivery of consumer goods; packaging of goods for transport
Computer services, namely providing search engines for locating information, resources, and goods on a global computer network




Perfect for these industries

Paper Goods and Printed Material
Advertising,  Business & Retail Services
Transportation & Storage Services 
Computer & Software Services & Scientific Services





Words that describe this mark
