This is a brand page for the BOOKNOOK trademark by The Book Nook, Inc. 
                                in Pacific Palisades, CA, 90272.
Write a review about a product or service associated with this BOOKNOOK trademark.    
                                Or, contact the owner The Book Nook, Inc. of the BOOKNOOK trademark by filing a request to communicate with    
                                the Legal Correspondent for licensing, use, and/or questions related to the BOOKNOOK trademark.
                           






On Friday, May 18, 2012,  a U.S. federal trademark registration was filed for 
                        BOOKNOOK by 
                        The Book Nook, Inc., Pacific Palisades, CA  90272.
                        The USPTO has given the BOOKNOOK 
                        trademark serial  number of  85629332.  
                        The current federal status of this trademark filing is ABANDONED - FAILURE TO RESPOND OR LATE RESPONSE.
                        The correspondent listed for BOOKNOOK is 
                        
                        
                                            CHRISTOPHER CHATHAM of 
                                            CHATHAM & HOGAN, LLP,  2312 W. OLIVE AVE., SUITE D, BURBANK CA 91506 
                                .
                            The BOOKNOOK trademark is filed in the category of 
                            
                                    Paper Goods and Printed Material
                                , 
                                    Advertising,  Business & Retail Services
                                , 
                                    Transportation & Storage Services 
                                , 
                                    Computer & Software Services & Scientific Services
                                . 
                            The description provided to the USPTO for BOOKNOOK 
                            is Printed publications and printed matter, namely, magazines, journals, books, manuals, diaries, calendars, charts, and printed recipes sold as a component of meal plans, in the fields of health, healthcare, nutrition, diet, weight loss, exercise, fitness, menu planning, and a healthy lifestyle; printed instructional and teaching materials in the fields of health, healthcare, nutrition, diet, weight loss, exercise, fitness, menu planning, and a healthy lifestyle. 
                            





