Barnes & Noble Nook

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia
  (Redirected from Nook)

					Jump to:					navigation, 					search

"Nook" redirects here. For other uses, see Nook (disambiguation).
See also: Barnes & Noble Nook 1st Edition, Nook Simple Touch, Nook Color, Nook Tablet, and Nook HD

Barnes & Noble Nook

Developer
Barnes & Noble


Product family
Nook


Type
E-book reader


Release date
November 30, 2009; 7 years ago (2009-11-30)


Operating system
